{"tid":96312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Trump部三星Galaxys3被沒收了","createTime":"2017-01-26T17:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T15:31:10.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7797f15e2cb19d468890bc8f6cf627b8949418c8","tid":96312,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:26:35.000Z","msg":"跟愛牌說掰掰 川普三星電話被沒收 <br />\n2017年01月26日 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net//images/twapple/640pix/20170126/BN01/BN01_005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2F%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20170126%2FBN01%2FBN01_005.jpg&h=b6d89344&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為避免美國總統被監聽或被駭客入侵，川普上週五接任美國總統後，陪他打選戰的「忠實戰友」三星Galaxy隨之被「沒收」，川普被迫改用美國國家安全局（NSA）特製的高安全性電話。美國媒體指出，2015年中川普準備開始爭取共和黨提名他成為總統候選人至上週四這段期間，川普用他的三星電話在推特（twitter）發佈至少900則訊息。 <br />\n<br />\n有趣的是，川普已使用這支三星電話1年多，但他卻不斷宣揚「美國製造」。他在就職典禮上說：「Buy American, Hire American（買美國貨，顧用美國人）。」 <br />\n<br />\n文╱林文彬、圖╱《紐約時報》 <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/finance/20170126/37533912/hotdailyart_right\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Fappledaily%2Farticle%2Ffinance%2F20170126%2F37533912%2Fhotdailyart_right&d=aPukUiJMoaG1miLfv3%2Fqy3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=7431b430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/finance/20170126/37533912/hotdailyart_right</a>"},{"pid":"b8c25e4cb4d4bcdbb35066c79f88730bfa0577fe","tid":96312,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:28:51.000Z","msg":"佢乜都放晒上twitter 講, d 黑客洗鬼hack佢部機咩, follow佢都得啦<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬當年夠話政策會對公眾公開、透明化 <br />\n我諗透極都唔夠侵侵咁透掛 <br />\n佢直頭心嗰句都打埋出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3aa5501e2f28d12f6eabbf377177043a0e64fe","tid":96312,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":